latestPosts.caption:
It has been a wonderful journey of Miss Uttarakhand 2025 ✨

One filled with learning, laughter, and unforgettable moments.
I’ve had the joy of meeting so many incredible people, forming new bonds, and walking a path of growth I’ll cherish forever.

To everyone who crossed my path , thank you.❤️
For the conversations, the support, the silences we shared, and those spontaneous smiles — each meant more than words can express.

Miss Uttarakhand 2025 wasn’t just an experience it was a transformation.
A chapter of life that will echo in my heart for years to come.

Here’s to all the memories we’ve made, and to the many more journeys ahead.
Thankyou ❤️ 💫

latestPosts.caption:
As an official collaborator of Miss Uttarakhand 2025, DBS Global University introduced the prestigious title of Miss Bollywood – a celebration of elegance, culture, and the empowered spirit of today’s youth.

The special sash was awarded by Dr. Anjum Aggarwal, Vice President of DBS Global University, known for her inspiring leadership and unwavering commitment to uplifting the aspirations of young individuals.

Representing DBS at the event, Dr. Rashmi Negi played a key role in curating this impactful partnership, reflecting the university’s dedication to platforms that foster growth, creativity, and confidence.

We extend our heartfelt congratulations to all the winners and participants for their stellar performances and infectious energy. Your presence lit up the stage and set new standards of excellence!
